  "conditionals": 55,
  "created": "2025-10-15",
  "description": "E. coli defends against bacteriophage infection through multiple systems: Restriction-Modification (R-M) systems where restriction endonucleases cleave unmethylated foreign DNA while methyltransferases protect self DNA, and CRISPR-Cas adaptive immunity where Cas proteins integrate phage DNA sequences into CRISPR array, transcribe crRNAs, and use them to guide Cas nucleases to destroy matching phage DNA.",
  "id": "ecoli_phage_defense",
  "keywords": [
    "phage defense",
    "CRISPR",
    "Cas",
    "restriction enzyme",
    "methylation"
  ],
  "lastUpdated": "2025-10-15",
  "logicGates": {
    "and": 5,
    "not": 5,
    "or": 4
  },
  "mermaid": "graph TD\n    %% Phage Infection\n    A[Bacteriophage Attachment] --> B[Phage DNA Injection]\n    B --> C[Foreign DNA Enters Cell]\n    \n    %% OR Gate 1: Which Defense System?\n    C --> D{OR: Which<br/>Defense Active?}\n    D -->|R-M System| E[Restriction-Modification]\n    D -->|CRISPR-Cas| F[Adaptive Immunity]\n    D -->|Abortive Infection| G[Suicide System]\n    D -->|None| H[Infection Succeeds]\n    \n    %% R-M System Branch\n    E --> I[Foreign DNA Recognition]\n    I --> J{AND: DNA Unmethylated<br/>at Recognition Site?}\n    J -->|No - Methylated| K[DNA Protected]\n    J -->|Yes - Unmethylated| L[Restriction Enzyme Cleavage]\n    \n    L --> M{OR: Which<br/>Restriction Enzyme?}\n    M -->|EcoRI| N[GAATTC Site Cleavage]\n    M -->|EcoRV| O[GATATC Site Cleavage]\n    M -->|Other| P[Other Sequence Cleavage]\n    \n    N --> Q[Phage DNA Fragmented]\n    O --> Q\n    P --> Q\n    Q --> R[/DNA Degradation/]\n    R --> S([Phage Destroyed])\n    \n    %% Self DNA Protection\n    K --> T[Host DNA Methyltransferase]\n    T --> U[Recognition Site Methylation]\n    U --> V[Self DNA Protected]\n    V --> W([Host Survives])\n    \n    %% CRISPR-Cas Branch\n    F --> X{OR: Prior<br/>Exposure?}\n    X -->|No - First Infection| Y[Adaptation Phase]\n    X -->|Yes - Memory| Z[Interference Phase]\n    \n    %% CRISPR Adaptation\n    Y --> AA[Cas1/Cas2 Complex]\n    AA --> AB[Phage DNA Fragment Selection]\n    AB --> AC[Protospacer Selection]\n    AC --> AD{AND: PAM Sequence<br/>Adjacent?}\n    AD -->|No| AE[/Not Suitable/]\n    AD -->|Yes| AF[Spacer Integration]\n    \n    AF --> AG[CRISPR Array Expansion]\n    AG --> AH[New Spacer Added]\n    AH --> AI[Heritable Memory]\n    AI --> AJ[Future Protection Acquired]\n    \n    %% CRISPR Interference\n    Z --> AK[CRISPR Locus Transcription]\n    AK --> AL[Pre-crRNA Synthesis]\n    AL --> AM[Cas6 Endonuclease]\n    AM --> AN[crRNA Processing]\n    AN --> AO[Mature crRNAs]\n    \n    %% Cascade Complex Assembly\n    AO --> AP{AND: All Cas Proteins<br/>Present?}\n    AP -->|No| AQ[No Immunity]\n    AP -->|Yes| AR[Cascade Complex Assembly]\n    \n    AR --> AS[Cas8/Cas11/Cas7 Complex]\n    AS --> AT{AND: crRNA<br/>Loaded?}\n    AT -->|No| AQ\n    AT -->|Yes| AU[Active Surveillance Complex]\n    \n    %% Target Recognition\n    AU --> AV[Foreign DNA Scanning]\n    AV --> AW{AND: Spacer Match<br/>AND PAM Present?}\n    AW -->|No| AX[No Match - Scanning Continues]\n    AW -->|Yes| AY[Target Recognition]\n    \n    AY --> AZ[R-loop Formation]\n    AZ --> BA[Cas3 Helicase-Nuclease Recruitment]\n    BA --> BB[/Target DNA Degradation/]\n    BB --> BC[Phage Genome Destroyed]\n    BC --> BD([Phage Neutralized])\n    \n    %% Abortive Infection\n    G --> BE[Infection Detected]\n    BE --> BF[Toxin Activation]\n    BF --> BG[Cell Suicide]\n    BG --> BH[/DNA Replication Halted/]\n    BH --> BI[/Phage Cannot Replicate/]\n    BI --> BJ([Colony Protected])\n    \n    %% Failed Defense\n    H --> BK[Phage Replication]\n    BK --> BL[Progeny Phage Assembly]\n    BL --> BM[Cell Lysis]\n    BM --> BN([Infection Spreads])\n    \n    %% Self/Non-self Discrimination\n    V --> BO{OR: Target<br/>DNA?}\n    BO -->|Self| BP[Methylation Protects]\n    BO -->|Foreign| BQ[Restriction Cleaves]\n    BP --> W\n    BQ --> S\n    \n    %% Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n    style A fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style B fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style C fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style D fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style E fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style F fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style G fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style H fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style I fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style J fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style K fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style L fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style M fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style N fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style O fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style P fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style Q fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style R fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style S fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style T fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style U fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style V fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style W fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style X fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style Y fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style Z fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AA fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AB fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AC fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AD fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AE fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style AF fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AG fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AH fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AI fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AJ fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AK fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AL fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AM fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AN fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AO fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AP fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AQ fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AR fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AS fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AT fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AU fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AV fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AW fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AX fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AY fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AZ fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BA fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style BB fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style BC fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BD fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BE fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BF fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style BG fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style BH fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style BI fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style BJ fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BK fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style BL fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style BM fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style BN fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BO fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style BP fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BQ fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000",
